{"tid":1743274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［行動Post］和你塞東九龍の春袋","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:36:18.000Z","uid":21678,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6be980db78f87b5a73014577bd76f911278949ab","tid":1743274,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"由於紅隧收咗皮<br />\n而家每日上半晝，九龍長期 Keep 住塞車<br />\n想要確保交通暢順<br />\n就要小心保護交通春袋 - 餘下嘅兩條過海隧道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkjHuEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkjHuEP.jpg&h=56585686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界東(由上水至大圍)過港島<br />\n冇咗紅隧，就九成司機會經觀塘過東隧<br />\n而觀塘道同外圍嘅觀塘繞道<br />\n兩條大路會響藍田滙合<br />\n形成樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLROqda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLROqda.jpg&h=138081eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別嘅係<br />\n過咗藍田、未入東隧之前<br />\n可以駛出鯉魚門道迴旋處，轉入啟田道上藍田<br />\n換言之<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果鯉魚門道迴旋處如果塞咗<br />\n就會官塘道、以致全個東九龍過海嘅交通癱瘓！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1Ciyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1Ciyb.jpg&h=ba7d106b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而以之前嘅經驗<br />\n好快就會有交通警過嚟關心司機<br />\n問佢哋諗掂響咩出口離開<br />\n出錯出口嘅司機，其實可以兜一兜上去啟田道，好快就有另一個迴旋處掉頭<br />\n重新入去迴旋處思考人生<br />\n<br />\n所以各位司機大佬<br />\n響迴旋處一定要小心駕駛<br />\n轉線諗清楚先好出<br />\n千祈唔好太急呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqOJd6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqOJd6w.jpg&h=3994a85a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果觀塘塞死<br />\n好容易就會倒灌番獅隧同大老山<br />\n到時就冚球散<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSxJYyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSxJYyd.jpg&h=81d8d039&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以大家記住小心駕駛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff034324becf87df3adf77be220b4f13366b110","tid":1743274,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5621aa195ba39c274bdbc9726a517bab95974b","tid":1743274,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"西九龍比較多highway <br />\n似乎冇位春袋位<br />\n如果有手足諗到<br />\n快啲分享大家齊齊保護佢"},{"pid":"408fff582bff215ff9c25c7dabb99ddfb4daeb9c","tid":1743274,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"東九個位之前講過好多次，係極具戰略價值，不過奈何容易被觀塘、秀x坪、將軍澳曱甴屋夾擊，而且牛頭角曱甴屋會大量增援。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8998fb967a1f26d02b8baea1a535200aa3aa7fe6","tid":1743274,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"【黑色分化警告】對家用緊區選嚟做分化，千祈唔好中計！我要分化撚完全收皮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743019</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4785bd1b107695cc8d6ed24e95e820d089a03211","tid":1743274,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"一早就應該放棄大西北<br />\n主攻過海果兩條隧道"},{"pid":"1bacd2f3e629d8fe1e441faf5f17dd4b3da4f818","tid":1743274,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"408fff582bff215ff9c25c7dabb99ddfb4daeb9c","tid":1743274,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"東九個位之前講過好多次，係極具戰略價值，不過奈何容易被觀塘、秀x坪、將軍澳曱甴屋夾擊，而且牛頭角曱甴屋會大量增援。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"所以一定要小心駕駛<br />\n唔好原地轉圈，咁大容易被人發現<br />\n兜兩個圈好上去藍田離開一下<br />\n跟住再排過<br />\n<br />\n加上而家紅隧塞咗<br />\n個威力＋１００％"},{"pid":"5129c318efa349c36cde89f6e6036173296f0ac2","tid":1743274,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm